30370/extras/GIF_close_gates_to_hell_FINAL.gif?t=1662416960\" /><br>Padre comes to assist the Halliwell family, who for generations have been keeping an earthly entrance to hell in check. The portal was quiet for far too long and such the residents of the mansion slowly forgot their task, thinking of their burden more as a fairy tale.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330370/extras/roguelite_shooting_action.png?t=1662416960\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330370/extras/GIF_roguelite_shooting_action_FINAL.gif?t=1662416960\" /><br>Descend into ever-changing dungeons that overflow with demonic enemies and pit your insane skills and over the top weapon collection against the satanic hordes. <br>Use an arsenal made of regular weapons using varieties of ammunition, holy weapons drawing on your faith, and unholy weapons craving for your blood. <br>Gain Blessing points to customize the skill tree that makes you stronger and gives you new useful miracles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330370/extras/defend_the_mansion.png?t=1662416960\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330370/extras/GIF_defend_the_mansion_FINAL.gif?t=1662416960\" /><br>Base defence sessions. When not busy dungeon-crawling, Padre Alexander will have to defend the mansion from waves of enemies both by using his skills and by building traps, global enchantments, and powerups.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330370/extras/voxel_inspired_minimalism.png?t=1662416960\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330370/extras/GIF_voxel_inspired_minimalism_FINAL.gif?t=1662416960\" /><br>While our protagonist got visibly smoother from the original The Padre, the voxel-inspired minimalist art style pervades the spooky environments as much as every character, monster and item.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330370/extras/perplexing_monsters.png?t=1662416960\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330370/extras/GIF_perplexing_monsters_FINAL.gif?t=1662416960\" /><br>A collection of monsters that are madder than the Mad Hatter, ranging from the possessed kitchen drawer to drunken long-dead pirate captains, passing through spooky insects and, of course, demons... a lot of demons. And unique bosses with an attitude.","developers":["Shotgun with Glitters"],"dlc":[1383600],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330370/header.jpg?t=1662416960","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"\u2018The Padre\u2019 and \u2018The Padre: One Shell Straight To Hell\u201d Copyright 2020, Shotgun With Glitters, all rights reserved. \u2018The Other Side\u2019 by The Feardemic Orchestra, composed by Brunon Lubas and Piotr Wozny, Copyright 2020, Feardemic s.p z o.o. \u201cThe Padre: One Shell Straight To Hell\u201d is published by Feardemic.","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256821784,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256821784/movie480.mp4?t=1612865956","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256821784/movie_max.mp4?t=1612865956"},"name":"Gameplay Overview","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256821784/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1612865956","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256821784/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1612865956","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com